name: Organic baby blue dress made in France by Lutin Lutinette
description:
Nice small "petrol" blue dress in a very original fabrics : 55 % hemp and 45 % cotton biological certified, the major model of the winter.
* hand-made babywear, unique example, French manufacturing.
* Ethical baby wear: Lutin Lutinette is also a work of the heart. I have elaborated this project with the goal of helping the families of autistic children.1€ put back in every sale to the association CERESA which brings an individual educational support and individualized to the children affected by autism.
* Dress decorated with a set of 3 flowers in Liberty fabrics and satin ribbons.
* Opening by the collar by a braid of Liberty fabrics for a maximal comfort of use.
* Finish of the collar by a way of Liberty fabrics.
